# ⚙️ 3. CODE SYSTEM (GitHub + Replit READY)

## 🐍 AUTO PROJECT CREATOR

```python
import os

structure = [
    "labs",
    "scripts",
    "detection-rules",
    "playbooks",
    "volumes",
    "pdf",
    "notes"
]

for folder in structure:
    os.makedirs(folder, exist_ok=True)

print("Blue Team Project Created!")
```

---

## 🐍 LOG ANALYZER (SOC SKILL)

```python
log_file = "logs.txt"

with open(log_file, "r") as f:
    for line in f:
        if "failed" in line.lower():
            print("⚠️ Suspicious:", line)
```

---

## 🐍 SIMPLE ALERT SYSTEM

```python
def detect_attack(log):
    if "unauthorized" in log.lower():
        return "ALERT: Possible intrusion!"
    return "OK"

print(detect_attack("Unauthorized login attempt"))
```

