# ⚠️ VERY IMPORTANT (READ THIS)

GitHub is powerful BUT:

* Some repos may contain malware or unsafe code
* Always:

  * Read README
  * Check stars & contributors
  * Don’t run unknown scripts blindly

👉 There are real cases of malware hidden in repos ([WIRED][7])

